<BlogPost
  title="How to set up AGENTS.md for multi-agent development workflows"
  description="AGENTS.md is becoming the standard way to configure AI coding agents across tools. Here is how to write one that works, with practical examples for different project types."
  date="April 11, 2026"
  readTime="10 min read"
